          <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Improving Transparency and Accuracy in Medicare Part D Spending Act</strong></p> <p>This bill amends title XVIII (Medicare) of the Social Security Act to prohibit Medicare Prescription Drug Plan sponsors from retroactively reducing payment on clean claims submitted by pharmacies. (A "clean claim" is a Medicare claim that is free&nbsp;of defects such as incomplete documentation.)</p>]]></text>
